sequenceDiagram
    participant SQS as SQS Queue
    participant W as Printer Worker
    participant DDB as DynamoDB
    participant S3 as S3

    loop Every 20s (long poll)
        W->>SQS: ReceiveMessage(WaitTimeSeconds=20)
        SQS-->>W: Message {jobId, s3Key}
    end
    W->>DDB: UpdateItem(SET status=PROCESSING WHERE status=RELEASED)
    alt Condition succeeds
        DDB-->>W: OK
        W->>S3: GetObject(s3Key)
        S3-->>W: Document bytes
        W->>W: Simulate printing (5-15s)
        W->>DDB: UpdateItem(SET status=DONE WHERE status=PROCESSING)
        DDB-->>W: OK
        W->>SQS: DeleteMessage
    else Already processed (idempotent skip)
        DDB-->>W: ConditionalCheckFailedException
        W->>SQS: DeleteMessage
    end
